data.text: @bchapman151 People will soon start to see and wake up from the HEX! They will learn how symbols can effect the subconscious mind. They will understand the true nature of reality and this nightmare will end!

@bchapman151 Hang in there! You did the right thing and we are approaching critical mass. Christ consciousness will lead us out of the darkness and God’s eternal love and light will make the world new! May God bless you and keep you on the path of righteousness!
